[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1132","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1132.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0779","title":"HP-UX SharedX recserv 程序拒绝服务漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统的 SharedX 组件中的 recserv 程序存在拒绝服务漏洞。未经认证的远程攻击者可通过向 recserv 服务端口发送特制网络请求，导致该服务崩溃或停止响应，影响 HP-UX 系统上 SharedX 功能的正常使用。该漏洞无需身份验证即可远程触发，攻击复杂度低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0779"],"sources":["cve","nvd"],"published":"1998-09-03","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"安装 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9810-086 中对应的 PHSS 补丁集。临时缓解措施：在防火墙或 TCP Wrappers 中限制对 recserv 服务端口的访问，仅允许受信任主机连接；如无需使用 SharedX 功能，建议直接禁用该服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9810-086"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1132.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1458","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1458.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1292","title":"Kolban Webcam32 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Kolban Webcam32 4.8.3 及更早版本的 Web 管理功能中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送超长 URL 请求触发该漏洞，导致任意命令执行。攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，可完全控制受影响的 Webcam 服务系统。该漏洞影响 Webcam32 4.8.3 及之前所有版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，建议用户升级至最新版本或禁用 Web 管理功能。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1292"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:07.593","remediation":"Kolban Webcam32 4.8.3 及更早版本均受此漏洞影响，且产品已停止维护，不存在官方补丁。建议立即停用 Kolban Webcam32，迁移至其他仍受支持的 Web 摄像管理软件。若无法立即停用，需在防火墙层面限制对 Web 管理端口（默认 80/TCP）的访问，仅允许受信任的管理 IP 地址连接，并避免将管理界面暴露在公网。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://xforce.iss.net/alerts/advise7.php","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1366","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1292.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1292","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1292.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1292.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hvvr-gqpw-hwhw/GHSA-hvvr-gqpw-hwhw.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87852/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1292.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--af40e1a5-c7b5-4a2b-b951-5e2b426ace33.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1458.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1147","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1147.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0792","title":"路由 ROUTERmate 默认 SNMP 社区名称漏洞","description":"ROUTERmate 路由器设备使用了默认的 SNMP 团体名（community name），未进行修改。SNMP 协议依靠团体名进行简单的身份认证，由于该默认团体名公开且未变更，未经身份认证的远程攻击者只要能够网络访问目标设备的 SNMP 服务（通常为 UDP 161 端口），即可利用该默认团体名与该设备建立会话，进而读取设备信息或发送写请求修改其配置（如更改路由、DNS 或管理设置）。该漏洞影响所有使用出厂默认配置的 ROUTERmate 设备，攻击无需本地权限或用户交互，危害程度中等，建议管理员立即修改默认 SNMP 团体名并限制访问来源。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0792"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:04.053","remediation":"立即修改 ROUTERmate 默认 SNMP 社区字符串为强密码，并在防火墙/ACL 限制仅允许可信管理 IP 访问 SNMP 端口（UDP 161/162）；若不再使用 SNMP 管理功能，建议在设备配置中完全禁用 SNMP 服务。由于该产品已停止维护，无可用升级版本，建议尽快替换为受厂商支持的网络设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www2.merton.ox.ac.uk/~security/rootshell/0022.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0283d468fcc07a0a091bff7d6aca02552e8d0048/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0792.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0792","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0792.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f7f250b0cc5cc23741447612a2f182f04c36db78/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0792.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7c8j-r54x-ccvc/GHSA-7c8j-r54x-ccvc.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/2014/gb_snmp_get_community.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0792.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000360.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4436c134-ab03-458c-bf2d-1dc4dfe83278.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1147.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0517","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0517.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0310","title":"HP-UX SSH 访问控制漏洞","description":"SSH 1.2.25 在 HP-UX 系统上存在访问控制缺陷，当系统添加新用户账户时，攻击者可通过 SSH 服务绕过认证直接访问这些新创建的账户，导致未授权访问。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 上运行的 SSH 1.2.25 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。漏洞源于用户账户创建后的默认配置未能正确限制访问权限，远程攻击者无需认证即可利用此漏洞获取系统访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0310"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:07.497","remediation":"升级至 OpenSSH（推荐 3.0 以上版本），禁用 SSH 1 协议，仅启用 SSH 2 协议。HP-UX 用户应安装 Hewlett-Packard 官方 SSH 安全补丁，或在系统层面通过 inetd.conf 禁用 SSH 服务，改用 telnet（如必要）并配合 hosts.allow/deny 限制访问来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0310","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d39c6fc359564f87c4fbc1b2c3e7c679c878fdd9/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0310.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0310","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0310.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0310.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6pm3-f7gw-pq5v/GHSA-6pm3-f7gw-pq5v.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0310.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82268/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d1259ae4-fae5-4ac0-a1f4-f0df5a94db65.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0517.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0502","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0502.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0302","title":"Sun Solaris FTP 客户端远程命令执行漏洞","description":"SunOS/Solaris 系统的 FTP 客户端存在命令执行漏洞，恶意 FTP 服务器可通过向客户端返回特制的响应数据包，诱使目标系统执行任意命令。攻击者无需认证即可远程触发该漏洞，完全控制受影响系统的 FTP 客户端进程。该漏洞影响 SunOS/Solaris 系列操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，建议用户及时升级相关补丁。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0302"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:06.490","remediation":"建议升级 SunOS/Solaris 至厂商修复版本（如 Solaris 2.6 补丁 105490-05 及更高），或使用替代 FTP 客户端（如 OpenBSD ftp、lftp）替换默认 /usr/bin/ftp。若无法升级，可在 ftp 客户端环境变量 FTPMODE 设为 passive 降低风险，同时限制出站 FTP 连接至可信服务器，并在网络层面阻止连接恶意外部 FTP 服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/176"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0502.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0332","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0332.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0162","title":"多厂商 FTP 服务器 安全绕过漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 访问控制列表（ACL）的\"established\"关键字用于匹配已建立 TCP 连接的回程流量，但其实现存在安全绕过漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标设备发送设置了 ACK 或 RST 标志位的特制 TCP 数据包，绕过 ACL 过滤规则，非授权访问受保护的内部网络资源。该漏洞影响多款 Cisco 路由器及交换机设备的 IOS 系统，CVSS v2 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0162"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-09-01","updated":"1998-09-01","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至不受影响版本。若无法升级，避免在 ACL 中单独依赖 established 关键词作为唯一过滤条件，应结合具体端口/协议/方向的多层访问控制规则，并部署防火墙进行深度包检测（stateful inspection）以防止伪造 ACK 包的绕过攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0332.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0327","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0327.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0158","title":"Cisco PIX Firewall Manager 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Cisco PIX 防火墙管理器（PFM）运行于 Windows NT 系统时，其 8080 端口存在未授权访问漏洞。远程攻击者可在已知目标文件名及路径的条件下，通过向 8080 端口发送 HTTP 请求获取任意文件内容，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响早期 Cisco PIX 防火墙管理软件，无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0158"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-08-31T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:43.470","remediation":"升级 Cisco PIX Firewall Manager 至 4.2(2) 或更高版本，或安装 Cisco 提供的安全补丁（参见 Cisco 安全公告）。作为临时缓解措施，在防火墙和主机层面限制对 PFM 服务器 TCP 8080 端口的访问，仅允许受信任的管理 IP 连接。鉴于 Cisco PIX 及 Windows NT 均已停止维护，建议尽快迁移至受支持的安全平台。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/pixmgrfile-pub.shtml","http://www.osvdb.org/685"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0327.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0164","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0164.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0065","title":"Sun Solaris CDE dtmail 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Solaris CDE 桌面环境中的 dtmail 邮件客户端在处理邮件附件时存在多个缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标用户发送带有特制附件的邮件，当受害者使用 dtmail 打开或预览邮件时，附件处理过程中的边界检查不足导致缓冲区溢出，攻击者可利用该漏洞在目标系统上以当前用户权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响运行 CDE 桌面环境的多个 Solaris 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0065"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-08-31T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:29.723","remediation":"立即安装 Sun（现 Oracle）提供的对应 Solaris 版本补丁（如 Sun 公告 00172 / 00173），将 CDE dtmail 升级到修补后的版本。如无法打补丁，建议禁用 dtmail 或限制其仅监听本地回环地址，并移除 setuid 权限以降低提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/181"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0164.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1299","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1299.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1041","title":"SCO OpenServer 5.0.5 本地堆栈溢出漏洞","description":"tags as required.<value>SCO OpenServer 5.0 和 SCO UNIX 3.2v4 系统中的 mscreen 程序存在本地堆栈缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可通过设置超长的 TERM 环境变量或在 .mscreenrc 配置文件中写入超长条目来触发该溢出，从而在本地获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SCO OpenServer 5.0.5 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。由于需要本地访问权限才能利用，攻击者需先获得系统的普通用户账户。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1041"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-08-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:34.940","remediation":"建议升级至 SCO OpenServer 5.0.7 或更高版本（含官方补丁 SCO-1999.001），或迁移至受支持的现代操作系统。临时缓解：移除 /usr/bin/mscreen 的 setuid root 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/mscreen），限制 TERM 环境变量长度（export TERM=vt100），限制用户写入 ~/.mscreenrc 权限（chmod 644 ~/.mscreenrc）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90686250717719&w=2","http://www.cert.org/vendor_bulletins/VB-98.10.sco.mscreen","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/10420","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1f3f1d799c1c9e44bc999093e18341513cabfa3f/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1041.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1041","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1041.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/fb79aaf8eeeb3ec551114292cd7a8693e166aee6/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1041.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6da213119b3c54637329347c0dc42c66b8a84f0a/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-xm8j-jw8c-j4ww/GHSA-xm8j-jw8c-j4ww.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/1999/CVE-1999-1041.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--11db4952-bc8b-4b8e-a026-44679b45b8a8.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1299.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0326","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0326.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0157","title":"Cisco IOS IP Fragmentation 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 的 IP 分片重组处理逻辑存在缺陷，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标路由器发送特制的 IP 分片数据包，触发设备在处理分片重组时进入死循环或异常状态，导致路由器崩溃、重启或停止响应正常流量。该漏洞影响 Cisco IOS 11.2p、11.3t、12.0、12.0t 等版本，无需身份认证即可远程触发，危害等级高危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0157"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-08-18","updated":"1998-08-18","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至 12.1 及以上版本，或升级 PIX Firewall 软件至 5.0 及以上版本；在接口配置 `ip virtual-reassembly` 命令启用虚拟分片重组功能以抵御分片攻击；配置 CBAC 时启用分片检查（`ip inspect name` 配合分片超时参数）；无法升级时可在边界 ACL 中拒绝异常分片包（如非初始分片且偏移量过小的包）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0326.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1451","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1451.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1283","title":"Opera Opera Web Browser 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Opera 3.2.1 浏览器存在 URI 解析拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向用户发送包含畸形 HTTP 标签（如 `http:///` 格式，含多余斜杠）的特制 URL，当用户点击该链接时，浏览器解析异常导致程序崩溃。该漏洞影响 Opera 3.2.1 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，属于低复杂度攻击，但仅造成拒绝服务，无法实现代码执行。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1283"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-08-14T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:06.420","remediation":"升级 Opera 浏览器至 3.3 或更高版本。该漏洞在后续版本中已修复，程序会正确解析含多余斜杠的 URL。如无法升级，建议换用现代浏览器（如 Firefox、Chrome）替代过时版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/10320","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1541","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1283.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1283","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1283.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1283.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-px2w-hxv5-5ppw/GHSA-px2w-hxv5-5ppw.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1283.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000354.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--3702305e-e771-4ff3-855f-92d91940bc90.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/be7ad03fdf3a412f0fd57a25f1732dc0ecfb1cb3/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1451.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1451.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0328","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0328.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0159","title":"Cisco IOS ICMP 不可达消息拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 存在拒绝服务漏洞。具有交互式命令行访问权限（如登录提示符）的攻击者，可通过向受影响设备发送特制命令序列，触发设备内核崩溃或重启，导致拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Cisco IOS 9.x、10.x 及 11.x 系列版本，攻击前提是已获取设备的交互式访问权限（如 Telnet/SSH 登录后的 CLI 环境），属于需要一定认证条件的本地拒绝服务漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0159"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-08-12","updated":"1998-08-12","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至 12.0 或更高版本以修复此漏洞。若无法升级，应在路由器上限制交互式访问权限，仅允许受信任的管理 IP 地址通过 SSH 或带外管理接口登录，并配置 ACL 过滤可疑 TCP RST 报文作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0328.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1389","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1389.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1199","title":"Apache HTTP Server 1.3.1 MIME 头部拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Apache HTTP Server 1.3.1 及更早版本存在 MIME 头部解析拒绝服务漏洞（又名 Sioux 漏洞）。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送大量同名 MIME 头的恶意 HTTP 请求，导致服务器资源耗尽而无法响应正常请求。该漏洞影响所有运行 Apache 1.3.1 及之前版本的系统，无需认证即可远程利用，CVSS v2.0 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。建议升级至 Apache 1.3.2 或更高版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1199"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-08-07","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Apache HTTP Server 至 1.3.2 或更高版本（该漏洞已在 1.3.2 中修复）。若无法升级，可在 httpd.conf 中通过 LimitRequestFields 指令限制单个请求允许的 HTTP 头字段数量，防止资源耗尽。建议直接升级至 2.4.x 最新稳定版以获得全面安全支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90252779826784&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90276683825862&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90280517007869&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90286768232093&w=2","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh51-errata-general.html#apache"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1389.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1389.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0446","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0446.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0262","title":"Hylafax 4.0 pl2 Faxsurvey CGI 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Hylafax 4.0 pl2 的 faxsurvey CGI 脚本未对用户输入进行有效过滤，远程攻击者可通过在查询字符串中注入 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等）实现任意命令执行。该漏洞影响 Linux 平台上的 Hylafax 4.0 pl2 版本，攻击者无需身份认证，只需向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可触发，可能导致服务器完全受控。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0262"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-08-04T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.590","remediation":"升级到 Hylafax 4.1 或更高版本，移除或禁用 faxsurvey CGI 脚本，限制 CGI 目录的执行权限，在 Web 服务器层面过滤传入 query string 中的 shell 元字符（如 `;`、`|`、`$`）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/2056","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1532","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20462","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0262.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0262","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0262.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0262.json","https://github.com/swimlane/soc-faker/blob/361c4ae88956878fbd8aaf5975044328556dfecd/socfaker/data/alert_names.txt","https://github.com/decal/werdlists/blob/81edb463f7f6311c85defefaf75ac9cd58e5cfb9/exploit-info/symantec-attack-signatures.txt","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/6723edd43ced2a9627d0c0e8bf12d208cfde84d5/sara/PLIST","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0262.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0446.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0161","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0161.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0062","title":"OpenBSD chpass 文件描述符泄漏本地权限提升漏洞","description":"OpenBSD 系统中的 chpass 命令存在文件描述符泄露漏洞，本地普通用户可利用该漏洞获取 root 权限。由于 chpass 在处理用户密码更改操作时未正确管理文件描述符，攻击者可通过精心构造的调用方式使进程泄露高权限文件句柄，从而实现对系统的完全控制。该漏洞影响 OpenBSD 2.x 及更早版本，需本地账户访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0062"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-08-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:29.320","remediation":"立即应用 OpenBSD 2.3 errata 004 号补丁，该补丁修复了 chpass(1) 的文件描述符泄漏问题，阻止攻击者篡改 /etc/master.passwd。如运行更低版本（2.2 及之前），应升级至至少 2.3 版本并应用全部安全补丁。临时缓解措施：严格限制本地用户登录权限，仅授予可信用户 shell 访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/7559"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0161.toml"}]